---
description: Do not add Cursor attribution to git commits or PRs
alwaysApply: true
---

Never add any of these to commits, PRs, or code comments:
- `Co-authored-by: Cursor`
- `Co-authored-by: cursoragent@cursor.com`
- `Made-with: Cursor`
- `--trailer` related to Cursor attribution

When creating git commits, use only the intended subject/body. Do not pass `--trailer` for Cursor.
